INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS FOR Hdbextractor++ library

1. Building the hdbextractor core library

1a. Dependencies: mysql and mysql development files

1b. Build the library:

    cd hdbextractor/trunk

    ./configure --prefix=/usr/local/hdbextractor++  (or wherever you like)

    make

    make install

1c. Build the documentation

    make doxygen-doc

    pdf  documentation: doc/hdbextractor.pdf
    html documentation: doc/html
